Resource Profile:

Official URL: http://koppeltaal.nl/fhir/StructureDefinition/KT2Practitioner Version: 0.8
Draft as of 2023-01-24 Responsible: VZVZ Computable Name: KT2_Practitioner

The (FHIR) Practitioner (resource) is a representation of a person who is directly or indirectly involved in the provision of health care.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: KT2_CareTeam and KT2_Task
